478
00:35:14,786 --> 00:35:17,387
Omona!

479
00:35:17,387 --> 00:35:20,291
Lihat ini. Ada 3 timun tersisa.

480
00:35:20,291 --> 00:35:22,880
Ini jelas tanda-tanda. Lakukan!

481
00:35:53,371 --> 00:35:55,838
<i>Hari ini hari yang berat.</i>

482
00:35:56,510 --> 00:35:58,422
<i>Kakiku gemetaran.</i>

483
00:35:59,503 --> 00:36:03,527
<i>Aku memakai sepatu hak tinggi, jadi
