484
00:36:05,217 --> 00:36:08,393
<i>Aku tahu kalau aku yang terburuk.</i>

485
00:36:08,393 --> 00:36:10,173
<i>Aku melakukannya, tapi...</i>

486
00:36:11,525 --> 00:36:13,771
<i>Akan kuberi kesempatan terakhir.</i>

487
00:36:15,655 --> 00:36:17,842
<i>Datanglah padaku segera.</i>

488
00:36:19,744 --> 00:36:21,199
<i>Sekarang.</i>

489
00:36:28,619 --> 00:36:31,445
Di musim dingin, ugh sumpah.

490
00:36:32,103 --> 00:36:35,599
