- Baik.

591
00:49:40,655 --> 00:49:41,875
Eonnie.

592
00:49:41,875 --> 00:49:44,534
Tidak bisakah aku beli sepatu dulu
sebelum mengembalikannya?

593
00:49:44,534 --> 00:49:46,443
- Kumohon!
- Aigoo...

594
00:51:05,003 --> 00:51:06,474
Yoo Ri.

596
00:51:42,146 --> 00:51:43,867
<font color="#00ff40"><b>[EVERGREEN </b></font> / <font color="#ff80c0"><b>THAT MAN OH SOO]</b></font>

597
00:51:43,867 --> 00:51:45,621
<i>Pewaris tidak diizinkan jatuh cinta...</i>

598
00:51:45,621 --> 00:51:48,117
<i>...dengan siapa pun yang 
mencerna serbuk sari.</i>

599
00:51:48,117 --> 00:51:50,264
<i>Itu adalah Hukum Pohon.</i>

600
00:51:51,088 --> 00:51:52,635
<i>Dan jika aku melanggarnya...</i>

601
00:51:52,635 --> 00:51:54,967
